        <p>Here's the honest warning: parrot eggs are fragile cargo, and jostling, cold, or delay can end development even with perfect packing. If you live within 2–3 hours of Midland, TX, we'll steer you to <a href="/contact-us/">local pickup</a> instead — the gentlest handoff a fertile egg can get.</p>

